ZH: 这座水库是向村庄供水的重要来源。
EN: This reservoir is an important source of water for the village.

ZH: 在大雨过后，水库水位上涨了。
EN: After the heavy rain, the water level of the reservoir rose.

ZH: 这座水库已经建成多年，一直供应着城市的用水需求。
EN: This reservoir has been built for many years, continuously supplying the city's water needs.

ZH: 我们需要保护水库的水质，以确保供水安全。
EN: We need to protect the water quality of the reservoir to ensure water safety.

ZH: 水库周围的环境非常美丽，吸引了很多游客。
EN: The surroundings of the reservoir are very beautiful, attracting many tourists.

ZH: 这座水库是农田灌溉的主要水源。
EN: This reservoir is the main source of water for irrigation in the farmland.

ZH: 水库的设计有助于防止洪水的发生。
EN: The design of the reservoir helps prevent flooding.

ZH: 山上的水库水质非常清澈，适合供应饮用水。
EN: The water quality of the reservoir on the mountain is very clear, suitable for supplying drinking water.

ZH: 水库的建设需要大量的资金和人力。
EN: The construction of the reservoir requires a large amount of funds and manpower.

ZH: 水库的周围种满了树木，有助于保护水源。
EN: The reservoir is surrounded by trees, which helps protect the water source.

ZH: 这座水库的存水量已经接近饱和。
EN: The storage capacity of this reservoir is close to saturation.

ZH: 水库的大坝已经修复完成，水位得以保持稳定。
EN: The dam of the reservoir has been repaired and the water level has been maintained stable.

ZH: 水库清澈见底，生态环境良好。
EN: The reservoir is clear and has good ecological environment.

ZH: 靠近水库的地方有一家旅馆，供游客休息。
EN: There is a hotel near the reservoir for tourists to rest.

ZH: 水库的管道需要定期检查，确保供水正常。
EN: The pipelines of the reservoir need regular inspection to ensure normal water supply.

ZH: 这座水库属于国家级重要水利工程。
EN: This reservoir is a national important water conservancy project.

ZH: 水库的水位在干旱季节会下降。
EN: The water level of the reservoir will decrease during the dry season.

ZH: 水库的建设为周围农村带来了经济效益。
EN: The construction of the reservoir has brought economic benefits to the surrounding rural areas.

ZH: 这座水库的规模庞大，是当地的地标之一。
EN: The scale of this reservoir is huge, making it one of the landmarks in the area.

ZH: 水库的管理需要科学技术支持，以提高效率。
EN: The management of the reservoir needs scientific and technological support to improve efficiency.
